# {{ app_name_title }}

Built with [Arvel](https://github.com/mohamed-rekiba/arvel) — async-first, type-safe Python web framework.

## Getting started

### Install dependencies

```bash
uv sync
```

### Run the dev server

```bash
arvel serve
```

The app starts at [http://127.0.0.1:8000](http://127.0.0.1:8000).

### Database

```bash
arvel db migrate    # Run migrations
arvel db seed       # Seed data
arvel db fresh      # Drop, recreate, migrate, and seed
```

### Tests

```bash
pytest tests/ -v
```

### Code quality

```bash
ruff check .        # Lint
ruff format .       # Format
```

## Project structure

```text
{{ app_name }}/
  bootstrap/            # Application factory and service providers
  config/               # Configuration modules (app, database)
  app/
    http/controllers/   # HTTP controllers
    http/requests/      # Request validation
    http/resources/     # API resources
    models/             # Data models
    observers/          # Model observers
    providers/          # Service providers
    events/             # Event classes
    listeners/          # Event listeners
    jobs/               # Background jobs
  tests/                # Test suite
  database/             # Migrations and seeds
  storage/              # File storage
```
